sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as Platform Orchestrator<br/>(rhods-operator)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Workbenches Controller<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant WBNamespace as Workbench Namespace<br/>(opendatahub / rhods-notebooks)

    Note over Orchestrator,Controller: Flow 1: Workbenches Reconciliation

    Orchestrator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Workbenches CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer token<br/>Spec: gatewayDomain, platform, mlflowEnabled
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event: Workbenches CR changed

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Reconciliation Loop

        Controller->>K8sAPI: GET Workbenches CR "default"<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Workbenches spec + status

        alt Management State = Managed
            Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Namespace (if not exists)<br/>Apply ownership label<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
            K8sAPI-->>Controller: Namespace created/exists

            Controller->>K8sAPI: List Deployments in workbench namespace<br/>label: app.opendatahub.io/workbenches=true<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
            K8sAPI-->>Controller: Deployment list + status

            Note over Controller: Compute kustomize params:<br/>section-title, mlflow-enabled, gateway-url

            Note over Controller: Evaluate conditions:<br/>Ready, ProvisioningSucceeded,<br/>Degraded, DeploymentsAvailable

            Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH Workbenches CR status<br/>conditions, phase, observedGeneration<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
            K8sAPI-->>Controller: Status updated

        else Management State = Removed
            Note over Controller: Component teardown<br/>(future implementation)
            Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH Workbenches CR status<br/>phase: Removed
        end
    end

    Note over Controller: Requeue with exponential backoff<br/>(5s base, 5m max)
